name: Roblox Page Previewer
description:
See how your Roblox ads, icons and thumbnails look in their actual webpage sizes, plus how they'll look when bundled with other Roblox content, all in Figma!


More detailed instructions are in the second page of the file.


Note: I am not affiliated with Roblox Corporation or any of their subsidiaries. This is an unofficial fan-made project purely made for fun.
